data.description: Welcome to paradise, 8 acres of waterfront property on Cedar Point just minutes from St Michaels.  The main house sits just off of the water on the point with magnificent water front views.  This house has been completely remodeled with 5 bedrooms, and 3.5 baths.  It has main floor living with 3 of the bedrooms being on the main floor, one of them being a tremendous owners suite that looks out over the water.  The floorpan is open with custom trim and finishes, high quality wood flooring and high ceilings throughout, dual living areas with their own fireplaces, a gourmet kitchen with wolf appliances, a massive quartz island and dining area that looks out over the water.  There is a large screened in deck, for enjoying your piece of paradise 3 seasons fo the year.  The second floor hosts two more bedrooms each with their own balcony, as well as a full bath, as well as tons of storage and the potential for more finished space.  The large yard that leads to the point ends in thousands of feet of shoreline and a pier for fishing or docking your boat, the water fluctuates from 3-7ft according to the tide.  Off of the main house is a detached two car garage with the potential for a second floor apartment. The second house on this property is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath rancher with a detached garage, and workshop.  This house is also move in ready and fully livable.  Across from this house is a water front kennel building that has its own bathroom, as well as a pole barn.  There is tons of potential here for all kinds of visions you may have.  This property is wonderful for fishing, boating, farming, waterfowl hunting and much much more!  Be sure to check out the neighboring listing at 6589 Cedar Cove Rd that is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath rancher on over 17 acres of waterfront.  Can be purchased as a package deal!
